title: Furnished 2b/2b - Utilities Included
posting_body: ['I have a furnished 2b/2b condo available for rent.', 'It is on the third floor with a two-floor plan with a fireplace and washer and dryer in the unit.', 'Rent is $1800.00 and includes water/sewer, heat, TV, internet, indoor warm garage with 2 parking spots, access to an indoor pool and gym, the only bill you will be responsible for is the electricity.', 'The condo is drugs and smoke free and that will not be negotiable.', 'The rooms are fully furnished with a queen bed (sheets and pillows included), nightstand, desk, and a 42"and 55” TV as showed in the pictures.', 'On the top floor is the master bedroom with a full bathroom and walk-in closet.', 'The second room is on the lower level and the ¾ bathroom is right next to it.', 'The living also has a 55” inch TV and it has a DVR included.', 'The Kitchen has the basics for your use, coffee machine, air fryer, mugs, glasses, plates, pot, and pans, etc…', 'The complex is Centrally located, you will have access on walking distance to bus lines, Centennial Park, Adams Hill Trail, Whole Foods, and many restaurants.', 'Also, the Airport, Southdale mall and Mall of America are as close as 10 mins drive.', "The security deposit is a full month's rent, your full deposit amount will be kept until move out, pending any damages to the residence.", 'We prefer 2 occupants, max 3.', 'The tenant must be responsible, clean, respect and take care of the place as their own.', 'The terms of the lease are 12 months, you will need to pass a background check, have references and a proof of income.', 'If you are interested, please send me an email telling me a little about yourself.']
